_sText:
This is a pretty big, underground jailbreak map.  It has the essentials with a timed cellblock opener, basic armory, and a big cellblock.

As far as games/activities to do, it has:Pool, Bhop, Soccer, Race, 4-Corners, Climb, Disco, Shot 4 Shot, Gun Toss

Explore the map and have fun on it.

Place the jb underrock v1.bsp in:
steamapps/<youraccountname>/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

When steampipe comes out, place in:
steamapps/common/Counter-Strike Source/cstrike/download/maps

Enjoy the jailbreak map.

Created by: Cpt. Hopi
